 TUI Library Rewrite - Full Implementation Plan                                                                                                                                         
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 Status: In Progress                                                                                                                                                                    
 Goal: Build @picro/tui from scratch by extracting and rewriting all components from pi-tui-legacy/ (both components/ and interactive/components/).                                     
 Constraints:                                                                                                                                                                           
 - NO code copying - must rewrite everything from scratch                                                                                                                               
 - Understand legacy architecture and APIs                                                                                                                                              
 - Create clean, modern library with all features                                                                                                                                       
 - All code stays in src/ - delete pi-tui-legacy/ when done                                                                                                                             
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 ────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────────                                                                                                       
                                                                                                                                                                                        
