 📋 Detailed Todo List                                                                                                                                                                  
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 ### Section A: Missing Components                                                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 #### A1. CountdownTimer                                                                                                                                                                
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 File: src/components/countdown-timer.ts                                                                                                                                                
 From: pi-tui-legacy/interactive/components/countdown-timer.ts                                                                                                                          
 Purpose: Display countdown in seconds, updates every second, callback on finish.                                                                                                       
 API to mimic:                                                                                                                                                                          
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 ```typescript                                                                                                                                                                          
   class CountdownTimer {                                                                                                                                                               
     constructor(                                                                                                                                                                       
       totalMs: number,                                                                                                                                                                 
       tui: TUI,                                                                                                                                                                        
       onTick: (secondsRemaining: number) => void,                                                                                                                                      
       onComplete: () => void                                                                                                                                                           
     );                                                                                                                                                                                 
     dispose(): void;                                                                                                                                                                   
   }                                                                                                                                                                                    
 ```                                                                                                                                                                                    
                                                                                                                                                                                        
 Implementation notes:                                                                                                                                                                  
 - Uses setInterval to calculate remaining seconds                                                                                                                                      
 - Calls onTick(seconds) every second                                                                                                                                                   
 - Calls onComplete() when time's up                                                                                                                                                    
 - dispose() clears interval                                                                                                                                                            
                                                                                                                                                                                        
